The Git repository for my website www.dailysteal.co.nz
A daily deal aggregator with support for scraping RSS feeds through FeedZirra.
-See /app/models/feed_entry.rb
--E.g.Console input: FeedEntry.update_from_feed("http://feed.1-day.co.nz/1-day")

Also supports screen-scraping through Nokogiri
-See Rake files in lib/tasks for examples.

Scheduling handled through the whenever gem.

Requires sendmail for feedback
